net.ljcomputing.entity

Interface PersistedEntity

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractPersistedEntity

    public interface PersistedEntity
extends Serializable
    Interface for entity classes. The interface ensures that there will be an id attribute for an entity.
    Author:
    James G. Willmore
